title: SEGA Games Pack for Android HD
description:
SEGA Games for Android

Version: 1.0

Language: en
Tablet: Not required

System Requirements: Android 2.3 and up

Installation: Installing the game on Android-powered device (smartphone, tablet)

1. Download the game (with the extension * .apk) and copy to the flash memory device.
2. Find the file and run it 
3. Find the icon of the game on Android-device
